```

16. Reset Factory ONU 
```
configure terminal 
%Info 20272: Enter configuration commands, one per line. End with CTRL/Z.
pon-onu-mng gpon-onu_1/2/2:17
restore factory
```

17. Restart ONU 
```
configure terminal 
%Info 20272: Enter configuration commands, one per line. End with CTRL/Z.
pon-onu-mng gpon-onu_1/2/2:17
reboot
```

